                      <div class="old-record-id-Hnand7rJBobMdJxhxkmc27rinQe nsa-accesstive">
                        A Yarbo Certified Refurbished product is a pre-owned unit that has undergone our rigorous,
                        factory-authorized refurbishment process. These units are thoroughly inspected, cleaned, and
                        tested to ensure they meet the same functional performance standards as a new Yarbo. While they
                        offer the same cutting-edge technology and intelligence, they come at a significantly more
