                    <div class="old-record-id-D7wVdXjosoAJkYxkvIPcQRCCnpc nsa-accesstive">
                      Grade B refers to the cosmetic condition of the unit. While 100% functionally equivalent to a new
                      machine, Grade B units may show minor signs of previous use, such as superficial scratches, light
                      scuffs, or minor surface discoloration on the outer shell. These imperfections are strictly
